Description.Text: The airport is within easy reach, while depending on traffic there are good connections to Moscow's centre as well. The nearest metro stop is Domodedovskaya, from which the centre can be reached in just over 20 minutes. MW (11/09)
The hotel is located in a business districts between Domodedovo Airport and the centre of Moscow.
The rooms are medium to large and are in fantastic condition.
There are two restaurants in the hotel, one serving Russian and European cuisine, the other Mediterranean cuisine.
The lobby is large with an open floor plan.
